KARAOKE SONG LIST CREATOR WITH DECEMBER 2013 UPDATE

Karaoke Song List Creator is a simple application that allows you to organize
your karaoke songs into lists to later print them. The program already comes with lots of karaoke tracks,
but of course, you can add your own CDs or songs. <a href="
http://www.airwer.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.airwer.com/</a>


PLEASE COPY AND PASTE THIS
HOW TO INSTALL
Please Follow Instructions

01. Install KSLC_Setup.exe first

02. Go to Start
Select, Control Panel; Folder Option; View; Hide extension for known
file Types (Remove the Tick from left Side); Apply; OK

03. Double Click the Full_Kar.exe file

04. Click Accept

If you installed Karaoke Song List Creator into a different folder than
the default (C:Program FilesKaraoke Song List Creator)
please change the Destination Folder before the next step.

05. Click Install.

After clicking Install Karaoke Song List Creator free/demo will be
instantly updated to the full version and the Setup window will close.

06. Restart your computer.

07. Once restarted double click the KSLC Data Dec2013.exe
to bring it up to the newest date.
